  "title": "Real Estate Agent",
  "description": "<p>We specialize in helping individuals and businesses find the perfect property in Singapore. Whether you're searching for a dream home, a strategic office space, or a high-potential investment, our team ensures a seamless journey from search to settlement.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>As we expand, we’re looking for passionate, driven, and entrepreneurial Real Estate Agents to join our dynamic team.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What's on Offer</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Access to Singapore’s most valuable propertie.</li>\n  <li>4 in 1 Compensation package (Basic salary + Transport allowance + Incentives + Commissions).</li>\n  <li>Full CPF Contributions.</li>\n  <li>Paid Annual Leave &amp; Sick Leave.</li>\n  <li>Free PropertyGuru Ad Slots, no out-of-pocket listing fee.</li>\n  <li>We handle your viewing schedules, you focus on closing deal .</li>\n  <li>No cold-calling, our leads are pre-qualified and ready to convert.</li>\n  <li>Dedicated support teams (marketing, admin, and legal experts) at your service.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist clients in selecting properties and achieving sales targets.</li>\n  <li>Promote property sales through various advertising media and listing services.</li>\n  <li>Engage with prospects and clients interested in real estate deals.</li>\n  <li>Communicate with clients to understand their property requirements and preferences.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate the closing process of property deals, ensuring all documents are signed and payments are received.</li>\n  <li>Act as an intermediary between property sellers and prospective buyers to facilitate transactions.</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with housing laws and policies during property transactions.</li>\n  <li>Monitor the property market to identify potential clients and secure brokerage deals.</li>\n  <li>Maintain ongoing contact with clients to discuss future business opportunities.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma or Bachelor’s Degree in a related field.</li>\n  <li>Valid CEA License or a Diploma/Graduate in Real Estate, with the ability to transact in the property market.</li>\n  <li>Flexibility to adapt to a dynamic market.</li>\n  <li>Strong oral and written communication skills.</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in liaising with Chinese-speaking clients.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
